text: you can’t connect apex domains like “<http://example.com|example.com>” to HubSpot, so we don’t have the ability to put URL mappings in place from <http://example.com|example.com> to anywhere else. If you have a service in place that redirects <http://example.com|example.com> to <http://www.example.com|www.example.com>, you can create url mappings that point from <http://www.example.com|www.example.com> to wherever you like
